text: Þis synt þa landgemæro æt Boclande & æt Welingtune.
Ærest uppan dune æt Achangran of Achangran adune on Sandford landgemære, þonne adune an þa ealdan dic, þanon oþ Sandford, þonne andlang þæs ealdan weges oþ Cytelwylle.
Of Cytelwylle andlang streames oþ Tan.
Adune andlang Tan streames oþ Bradanford.
Þanon on þeodherpoð oþ þa estas.
Þanon on land gemere oþ Stanford.
Þanon upp on Fiduc andlang landgemæres swa upp on Mær broc oþ Byrnan hris.
Þis synt þa land gemæro to Lidgerd.
Of Linlege uppon strem to Costanforda.
Of Cottanforda upon strem to Gosforda.
Of Gosford uppon strem to Stanforda.
Of Pytt apuldre on æst, Of æste adun cousled to Readanclife, of Readanclife to Ruwanbeorge, of Ruwanbeorge to Ludanwylle.
Uppon an slæd to Holan wege.
Of Holanwege uppon slæd to Bacganbeorge.
Of þam forda uppon stræm to Oxenagete.
Of þam forda adune on strem to Cunecanforda.
Of Suran apuldran oth hit cymth eft on Linlege.
